The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for relation extraction, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses cross-lingual projection, which falls under the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.NE).
